reviews.review_text: cool show nice jamming on Scar Beg

That Old Tank I wasn't at this or that years NYE if there was one? Not sure why, this is rather good. They do sound frog-gish, but at least they got a Hegenberger before the show. I recall it was spacious and I went back for something some other event and the spacious part was now a huge bar and it wasn't the same. Still it'd be cool to go there for 2016 NYE, if there is one. Set list of this is good and avoids some of the garbage they were doing then like wave to tha wind.. Glad I tried it, so far anyways, since I rarely listen to late stuff like 91-95
